<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Welcome to WorkNest</title>
<style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #2193b0, #6dd5ed);
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 600px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 { 
	        margin-bottom: 20px; 
	        color: #333; 
        }
        input {   
        	width: 100%; 
	        padding: 12px; 
	        margin: 10px 0; 
	        border: 1px solid #ddd; 
	        border-radius: 6px; 
        }
        .btn { 
	        width: 100%; 
	        padding: 12px; 
	        background: #2193b0; 
	        border: none; 
	        color: #fff; 
	        font-size: 16px; 
	        border-radius: 6px; 
	        cursor: pointer; 
        }
        .btn:hover { 
        	background: #176d7a; 
        }
        a { 
	        color: #2193b0; 
	        text-decoration: none; 
        }
    
    p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        color: #34495e;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to WorkNest</h1>
        <p>The ultimate platform for task management and team collaboration. It offers a seamless experience to organize, track, and complete your tasks efficiently.</p>
        <a href="login.jsp" class="btn">Get Start</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
